{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Hello SecurityexController!{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<style>
    .example-wrapper { margin: 1em auto; max-width: 800px; width: 95%; font: 18px/1.5 sans-serif; }
    .example-wrapper code { background: #F5F5F5; padding: 2px 6px; }
</style>

<div class="example-wrapper">
    <h1>Cviceni 11</h1>

    <p>Hey there. Let's do some practice on Security bundle!</p>
    <p>First of all, you can register new user by clicking on the link below.</p>
    <p><a href="{{ path('app_register') }}">Register</a></p>
    <p>or try to login if you are already registred user <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}">here</a></p>
    <p>By the way, only if you logged in you will see here secret message below!</p>
    <p>Secret message: <strong>
    {{ is_granted('ROLE_USER') ? 'You are ' ~ app.user.username ~ ' and you are logged in!' : 'You are not logged in!' }}
    </strong></p>
    <p>And if you want to logout, you can do it <a href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">here</a></p>

</div>
{% endblock %}
